---
---

<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero__decor" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="hero__float hero__float--1">⭐</span>
    <span class="hero__float hero__float--2">✨</span>
    <span class="hero__float hero__float--3">🎈</span>
    <span class="hero__float hero__float--4">⭐</span>
  </div>

  <div class="container hero__inner">
    <div class="hero__copy">
      <span class="badge">🐍 Untuk kamu yang baru mulai ngoding</span>
      <h1>Ngoding itu <span class="text-green">seru</span>, kok! Yuk kenalan sama Python.</h1>
      <p class="hero__desc">
        Belajar bahasa pemrograman Python dengan cara yang santai dan menyenangkan —
        tanpa istilah rumit, langsung praktik dari browser. Ditemani Pyto, si robot
        ular yang selalu siap membantu.
      </p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href="#bab-1" class="btn btn-primary">Mulai dari Bab 1 →</a>
        <a href="#editor" class="btn btn-secondary">▶ Coba Editor</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__stats">
        <div class="hero__stat">
          <strong>100%</strong>
          <span>Gratis</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__stat">
          <strong>Langsung</strong>
          <span>Coba di Browser</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero__art">
      <div class="hero__circle" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="hero__mascot-wrap">
        <span class="hero__speech">print("Halo!")</span>
        <span class="hero__mascot" role="img" aria-label="Pyto si robot ular melambai">🐍</span>
        <span class="hero__ready-badge">Ayo mulai! 🎉</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-block: 64px var(--section-spacing);
  }

  .hero__decor {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero__float {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 28px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    animation: floaty 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero__float--1 {
    top: 12%;
    left: 6%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .hero__float--2 {
    top: 22%;
    right: 10%;
    animation-delay: 1.2s;
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .hero__float--3 {
    bottom: 18%;
    left: 12%;
    animation-delay: 2.4s;
    font-size: 32px;
  }

  .hero__float--4 {
    bottom: 30%;
    right: 6%;
    animation-delay: 0.8s;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  @keyframes floaty {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-18px) rotate(8deg);
    }
  }

  .hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .hero__copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .hero__desc {
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size: 18px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .hero__stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .hero__stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .hero__stat strong {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--pyto-green-dark);
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .hero__stat span {
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .hero__art {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 380px;
  }

  .hero__circle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 340px;
    height: 340px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--pyto-green-soft) 0%,
      #d8f2fb 45%,
      #f4ecff 100%
    );
  }

  .hero__mascot-wrap {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .hero__mascot {
    font-size: 140px;
    animation: bob 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 24px rgba(30, 42, 50, 0.15));
  }

  @keyframes bob {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-14px);
    }
  }

  .hero__speech {
    position: absolute;
    top: 4px;
    right: -20px;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    color: var(--code-green);
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-code);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .hero__speech::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -6px;
    left: 24px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .hero__ready-badge {
    background: var(--pyto-green);
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(47, 191, 113, 0.3);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero__float,
    .hero__mascot {
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .hero__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero__copy {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero__actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero__stats {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero__art {
      min-height: 300px;
      order: -1;
    }

    .hero__mascot {
      font-size: 110px;
    }

    .hero__speech {
      right: 10px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero__speech {
      font-size: 12px;
      right: -6px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
    }
  }
</style>
